OL,3,CAccelerant poured through letterbox in
OL,4,C'targeted' arson attack
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after a
OL,7,Fsuspected arsonist poured an
OL,8,Faccelerant through the letterbox of a
OL,9,Fhome before setting it alight.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to a property on
OL,12,FGreat Hall Close, in Radcliffe, Bury,
OL,13,Fat approximately 2am on 4 April 2026,
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police said.
OL,16,FEmergency services confirmed that no
OL,17,Finjuries were sustained during the
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
