FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775484660
OL,3,CAccelerant poured through letterbox in
OL,4,C'targeted' arson attack
OL,6,FThe fire is currently being treated by
OL,7,Fpolice as a deliberate act but
OL,8,Fdetectives believe there is no
OL,9,Fimmediate danger to the local
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Niamh McCarthy,
OL,13,Ffrom Bury CID, said: "We understand
OL,14,Fthis incident may cause concern within
OL,15,Fthe community; however, our assessment
OL,16,Fis that it was a targeted attack, and
OL,17,Fthere is no risk to the wider public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775484660
OL,3,CAccelerant poured through letterbox in
OL,4,C'targeted' arson attack
OL,6,F"Our enquiries to identify those
OL,7,Fresponsible are ongoing, and we urge
OL,8,Fanyone with information that may
OL,9,Fassist our investigation to come
OL,10,Fforward."
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police is now
OL,13,Fappealing for witnesses or anyone with
OL,14,Frelevant footage to contact the force.
OL,16,FDetectives are particularly interested
OL,17,Fin CCTV or Ring doorbell footage
OL,18,Fmobile phone recordings and witness
OL,19,Faccounts from the Great Hall Close
OL,20,Farea around the time of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
